              <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                <locus to="88"/>
                <date when="1508" evidence="internal"/>
                <note>The colophon states that the manuscript was written in Jerusalem in the <date>Year of Grace 167 (1508 C.E.)</date>
                  by <persName ref="PRS11118Tewogolos">Tewogolos</persName>, a monk of the Convent of Sāmuʾel of gadāma Wāli while the superior was <persName ref="PRS11115FereKr">Fǝre Krǝstos</persName> of the order
                  of Takla Hāymānot, the magābi <persName ref="PRS11116GabraN">Gabra Nolāwi</persName> of the Convent of Sāmuʾel of gadāma Wāli and the qāyǝm
                  <persName ref="PRS11117Samuel">Sāmuʾel</persName> of the oder of Yonās. It is followed by a prohibition
                  of removing this manuscript from the <placeName ref="INS0323DAM">Convent of Minās</placeName>.</note>
                በአኰቴተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ተጽሕፈት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አመ፡ <date>፻፷ወ፯፡ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ በመዋዕለ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ አሜሃ፡ አበቅቴ፡ ፬፡
                  ወመጥቅዕ፡ ፳ወ፯፡ </date>ወተፈጸመት፡ በ<placeName ref="LOC3957Jerusa">ኢየሩሳሌም፡</placeName> ሀገረ፡ ሰላም። አመ፡ <date>፳ወ፭፡ ለመስከረም፡ በዕለተ፡ ዐርብ፡ ጊዜ፡<gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/> ሰዓተ፡</date>
                መዓልት። በመዋዕለ፡ ራይስ፡ <persName ref="PRS11115FereKr">ፍሬ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</persName> ወልደ፡ አቡነ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት። ወመጋቢ፡ <persName ref="PRS11116GabraN">ገብረ፡ ኖላዊ፡</persName> ወልደ፡ አቡነ፡ ሳሙኤል፡ ዘገዳመ፡ ዋሊ። ወቃይም፡ <persName ref="PRS11117Samuel">ሳሙኤል፡</persName> ወልደ፡ አቡነ፡ ዮናስ።
                ወጸሓፊሃኒ፡ ወልደ፡ አባ፡ ሳሙኤል፡ ዘገዳመ፡ ዋሊ፡ <persName ref="PRS11118Tewogolos">ቴዎጎሎስ፡</persName> ኃጥእ፡ ወአ<supplied resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">ባ</supplied>ሲ። ወእለ፩ አንበብክሙ፡
              </colophon>
